data.description: This beautiful home is situated on a spacious 5-acre lot, offering plenty of room for privacy and outdoor activities. As you enter the home, you are greeted by a spacious living room with large windows that allow for ample natural light with 3 beds and 2 full baths. This huge lot provides endless possibilities. Whether you want to create a beautiful garden, set up a playground for children, build, or simply enjoy the tranquility of nature, this property offers the space to fulfill your dreams. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and enjoy the peaceful lifestyle it offers. Buyer and buyer agents please do your due diligence. All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed.
